x. 25 blinis).","Place 1 heaped teaspoon of salmon mixture onto each blini. Top each blini with ½ teaspoon reserved beetroot and extra dill. Season to taste with salt and pepper before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Beetroot and salmon topping","content":["1000 g water","100 g raw beetroot, peeled and cut into small cubes (5 mm)","350 g fresh boneless, skinless salmon fillets","1 lemon, juice and zest only, no white pith","100 g watercress","1 tbsp Greek yoghurt","1 tbsp cream cheese","3 sprigs fresh dill, leaves only, plus extra for garnishing","¼ tsp salt","¼ tsp freshly ground black pepper"]},{"title":"Blinis","content":["2 tsp unsalted butter","150 g buckwheat flour","50 g wholemeal self-raising flour","1 level tsp baking powder","225 g full cream milk","1 egg","½ tsp sea salt, plus extra to season","olive oil spray, for frying","freshly ground black pepper, to season"]}],"id":"r116063","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-6jYclm1Ejwo\/XZarEM1B6_I\/AAAAAAAAhkk\/S1Dm1_Wd748Yi7RZPP9VVGV0xJcJ4EyWwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_zj12GOxvJb4h-X4M.png","title":"Poached salmon and beetroot blinis","publishedAt":"2016-08-21T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.28 g","fat":"4.25 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"5.94 g","calories":"358 kJ \/ 85 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, large frying pan, refrigerator, stove top","basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","25 portions"]}